How To Donate:

The HDMA Center has established a C-fund account, for donation purposes.


Donors can write a check ( payable to the Campanile Foundation ) with the memo to:

The Center for Human Dynamics in the Mobile Age fund MEMO “Metabolism of Cities Living Lab.”


At the following link:


This C-fund account is handled by the SDSU Research Foundation. The Fund Code is C04274.  


Please contact the HDMA Center Director and the Foundation Admin, Frank Sweeney for using this fund with several activities.
